1. *Bolnica* je mesto u kom se leče oboleli pacijenti. (The hospital is a place where the sick patients are treated.) 
2. On je proveo noć u *bolnici*. (He spent the night in the hospital.)
3. U *bolnice* se oboleli pacijenti primaju 24 časa dnevno. (The sick patients are admitted to the hospital 24 hours a day.)
4. *Bolnica* je opremljena najmodernijom medicinskom tehnologijom. (The hospital is equipped with the most modern medical technology.) 
5. Hitno je prevezen u *bolnicu*. (He was urgently taken to the hospital.)